data.value: Pokhara is a city in Nepal known for its natural beauty, with stunning views of the Annapurna mountain range and Phewa Lake. It is a popular starting point for trekking and adventure activities in the region.

data.value: Chitwan is a region in Nepal known for its national park, with diverse wildlife including tigers, elephants, and rhinos, attracting nature and adventure enthusiasts and is one of the popular destination in Terai.

data.value: Janakpur is a city in Nepal considered sacred to Hindus and a major pilgrimage site. It is believed to be the birthplace of Sita, a central figure in Hindu mythology. The city is home to several historic temples and monuments.

data.name: richTextBox8.Text
data.value: Mustang is located in the high Himalayas, known for its unique landscape and cultural heritage, including ancient monasteries, temples, and villages. It is also a popular destination for trekkers and adventure travelers.
